name: Zaenal Akbar
body:
### Welcome to My GitHub Page.
I am a Junior Researcher at the [Indonesian Institute of Sciences](http://www.lipi.go.id). My research interests are mainly in **Knowledge Discovery**, especially from **large-scale** databases.

Currently, I am working as Research Scientist at the [Semantic Technology Institute (STI) Innsbruck](http://sti-innsbruck.at), Austria.

[Personal Homepage](http://akbar.ilmuwan.org)
